  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Companion Appearance Enhancement</span>. This compact device generates detailed analytics reports of creature traversal habits, to provide explorers with insight into the secret lives of their animal companions.<br><br>Earn the trust of wild animals to adopt companions. Interact with companions to customise their appearance.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">同伴外观强化</span>。这种小巧的设备可以生成详细的生物穿越习性分析报告，帮助探险家深入了解其动物同伴的秘密生活。<br><br>赢得野生动物的信任来收养同伴。与同伴互动来自定义它们的外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特<span class=\"name name-stellar\">同伴外觀強化</span>。輕薄的裝置，針對生物移動習慣產出詳細分析報告，讓探險家能夠更深入瞭解動物同伴的祕密生活。<br><br>獲得野生動物的信任，即可收養為同伴。與同伴互動，自訂其外觀。"
  },
